          <p>Consistent activity over time. Not one perfect post. Not 50 reviews in a week. Regular posts, steady review acquisition, photos added over time, a profile that looks like it belongs to a business that is open and active right now.</p>
          <div class="tr-read-section" style="margin-top:12px;">The four-week cycle</div>
