<!-- OUTREACH SOP -->
<div id="sop-outreach" class="tp active">
<div class="card" style="padding:20px 22px;">
  <div class="ch"><div class="ci">&#128228;</div><div><div class="ct">Outreach SOP</div></div></div>
  <div class="sop-meta">
    <span class="sop-tag">Daily activity</span>
    <span class="sop-tag when">Use every working day</span>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">Steps</div>
  <div class="step-grid">
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">1</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Find leads — 20–30 mins</strong>Google Maps, target area. Filter: few reviews, no website, incomplete profile. Note the single biggest gap — that is your hook.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">2</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Send messages — 1 hour block</strong>30–50 per session. Personalise with trade + location every time. Never copy-paste identically all day.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">3</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Work replies — twice daily</strong>Mid-morning and end of day. Respond within the hour. Goal: book the call.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">4</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Send follow-ups</strong>No reply at 48h → Day 3–4 follow-up. Still nothing at 5 days → Day 7–8 exit. Max 3 messages total to any cold lead.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">5</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Book and confirm</strong>Specific day + time. Zoom link sent immediately. Reminder sent the evening before — not the morning of.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">Rules</div>
  <div class="rules-row">
    <span class="rule-tag hard">Max 3 messages to a cold lead</span>
    <span class="rule-tag hard">Reply within 5 mins or the window closes</span>
    <span class="rule-tag">One ask per message — then stop</span>
    <span class="rule-tag">No-show: one follow-up in 10 mins, then leave</span>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">Objection Handles</div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"Can you just text the info?" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">i would but it is a bit of a nightmare to explain over text. much easier to just tell you what to click while you are in the van. only takes 5 mins so you can sort it yourself. you free for a quick bell tomorrow?<div class="onote">Van time close. Stop there.</div></div></div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"How much will this cost?" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">nothing. i will literally just tell you what buttons to click so you can sort it yourself. we just help for free until you are so busy you would rather have us do the legwork. you around for 5 mins tomorrow?<div class="onote">Free frame first. One ask. Stop.</div></div></div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"I am too busy right now" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">totally get it. i will be brief. just call while you are driving between jobs so it does not get in the way. does 4pm work?<div class="onote">Van time. Specific time. One ask.</div></div></div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"Is this a sales pitch?" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">not at all. i will tell you what is missing and you can go fix it yourself. no credit card or anything. we just help for free until you decide you want it off your plate. sound fair?<div class="onote">"Sort it yourself" removes all fear.</div></div></div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"I already have a marketing guy" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">perfect. i will give you the list of gaps and you can just hand it to him. saves him the work and gets you more calls. you free for a quick chat tomorrow?<div class="onote">No threat. Just value.</div></div></div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label" style="margin-top:16px;">Scripts</div>
  <div class="scripts-wrap">
    <div class="script-item"><div class="script-label">Day Before Reminder</div><button class="scp" onclick="cpSOP(this)">Copy</button><div class="script-text">Hi [Name], just a reminder we have a call booked tomorrow at [time]. i will have your Google profile pulled up ready — should only take 15 minutes. see you then.</div></div>
    <div class="script-item"><div class="script-label">Morning Of Call</div><button class="scp" onclick="cpSOP(this)">Copy</button><div class="script-text">morning [Name], looking forward to the call at [time] today. speak soon.</div></div>
    <div class="script-item"><div class="script-label">No-Show (within 10 mins)</div><button class="scp" onclick="cpSOP(this)">Copy</button><div class="script-text">hey [Name], we had a call booked just now — no worries if something came up. want to find another 15 minutes this week?</div></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="padding:20px 22px;">
  <div class="ch"><div class="ci">&#129302;</div><div><div class="ct">Reply Generator</div><div class="cs">Paste their message — get a stage read and options</div></div></div>
  <textarea class="fi" id="rg-outreach-input" placeholder="Paste their message here..." style="min-height:60px;margin-bottom:10px;"></textarea>
