<!-- AUDIT SOP -->
<div id="sop-audit" class="tp">
<div class="card" style="padding:20px 22px;">
  <div class="ch"><div class="ci">&#128269;</div><div><div class="ct">Audit SOP</div></div></div>
  <div class="sop-meta">
    <span class="sop-tag">Before every Zoom call</span>
    <span class="sop-tag when">Also during outreach to find the hook</span>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">Pre-Call Steps</div>
  <div class="step-grid">
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">1</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Open Audit Tool + their GMB in separate tabs</strong>Fill in business name, trade, location. Check every field on their actual profile — do not assume.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">2</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Work through the checklist</strong>Tick what IS correct. Everything unticked is a finding. Priority: review count, photos, description, service area, website link.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">3</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Check their website on mobile</strong>Open on your phone. Loads fast? Phone visible? Clear CTA?</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">4</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Check their ranking (incognito)</strong>Search "[trade] in [location]". Map pack, page 1, or not showing?</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">5</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Generate internal report + set up pitch deck</strong>Get the score. Know the top 3 findings before you dial. One package recommendation ready.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">On The Call</div>
  <div class="step-grid">
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">6</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Open with discovery — 2 mins before sharing screen</strong>How do jobs come in? Quiet months? Looked at their own profile? Listen. Use it to land the findings harder.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">7</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Share screen — show their live profile + ranking</strong>"This is what someone sees when they search [trade] in [area] right now."</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">8</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Walk through each finding — pause after each</strong>Show the top competitor. Sit in silence. Do not fill it. The gap does the work.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">9</div><div class="step-text"><strong>One recommendation. One question. Stop.</strong>"Based on what we have looked at today — do you want us to handle this for you?"</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">10</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Send-Out within 30 mins of call ending</strong>Even if they said yes. Especially if they said yes.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">Rules</div>
  <div class="rules-row">
    <span class="rule-tag hard">Pitch deck open before the call — never during</span>
    <span class="rule-tag hard">Only one package recommendation</span>
    <span class="rule-tag">Silence after findings — do not fill it</span>
    <span class="rule-tag">Send-out within 30 mins of ending</span>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label" style="margin-top:16px;">Scripts</div>
  <div class="scripts-wrap">
    <div class="script-item"><div class="script-label">Call Opener</div><button class="scp" onclick="cpSOP(this)">Copy</button><div class="script-text">Good to speak with you [Name]. I have got your Google profile up on my screen — I am going to walk you through exactly what I found and what it means for your enquiries. This is not a pitch, it is just what is there. Sound good?</div></div>
    <div class="script-item"><div class="script-label">24 Hours After</div><button class="scp" onclick="cpSOP(this)">Copy</button><div class="script-text">Hi [Name], just following up from our call yesterday. Hope what we went through was useful. If you want to talk through the next step just reply here and we can pick it up.</div></div>
    <div class="script-item"><div class="script-label">4 Days After — No Reply</div><button class="scp" onclick="cpSOP(this)">Copy</button><div class="script-text">Hi [Name], checking back in on this. Every week that profile sits as it is, those enquiries go to someone else in [area]. If the timing is right I can get everything moving this week. If not, no problem — just let me know either way.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label" style="margin-top:16px;">Objections</div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"What does it cost?" (mid-call) <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">Let me show you the last couple of things first so the recommendation makes sense, then I will walk you through the options. Two more minutes.<div class="onote">Delay price until after findings. The audit justifies the fee.</div></div></div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"It is too expensive" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">completely understand. a well-run GMB brings in 5 to 15 extra jobs a month. at &#163;200 average that is &#163;1,000 to &#163;3,000 extra. we charge &#163;147 a month to manage the thing that generates that. does the value make sense when you look at it that way?<div class="onote">ROI frame. Ask if it makes sense. Stop.</div></div></div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"I need to think about it" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">of course — can I ask what specifically you want to think through? I would rather address it now while we are talking than have you go away with a question I could have answered.<div class="onote">Get the real objection. Do not let it float.</div></div></div>
  <div class="ob"><div class="oh" onclick="togO(this)">"I need to speak to my partner" <span class="oa">&#9660;</span></div><div class="obody">absolutely — when do you expect to speak to them? I will send you a summary of everything we looked at so you go into that conversation with something concrete.<div class="onote">Get a date. Send the send-out immediately.</div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="padding:20px 22px;">
  <div class="ch"><div class="ci">&#129302;</div><div><div class="ct">Reply Generator</div><div class="cs">Post-call replies</div></div></div>
  <textarea class="fi" id="rg-zoom-input" placeholder="Paste their reply..." style="min-height:60px;margin-bottom:10px;"></textarea>
  <button class="btn btnp" onclick="generateReply('zoom')" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:10px;">Generate Reply Options</button>
  <div id="rg-zoom-out" style="display:none;"></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- FOLLOW-UP CALL SOP -->
<div id="sop-followup" class="tp">
<div class="card" style="padding:20px 22px;">
  <div class="ch"><div class="ci">&#128222;</div><div><div class="ct">Follow-Up Call SOP</div></div></div>
  <div class="sop-meta">
    <span class="sop-tag">Every time a call is booked</span>
    <span class="sop-tag when">Booking → reminder → hand-off</span>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">Steps</div>
  <div class="step-grid">
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">1</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Qualify before booking</strong>Trades business? Have or want a GMB? Are they the decision-maker?</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">2</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Book, confirm, send Zoom link immediately</strong>Specific day and time. Link sent the moment it is booked.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">3</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Evening-before reminder</strong>"Just a reminder [Name] — on for [time] tomorrow. GMB pulled up ready. See you then."</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">4</div><div class="step-text"><strong>Hand off to closer with context</strong>Name, trade, location, main GMB weakness, anything they mentioned. Not just a name and a time.</div></div>
    <div class="step-row"><div class="step-pill">5</div><div class="step-text"><strong>No-show: one follow-up in 5 mins</strong>"Hey [Name], we had a call booked just now — no worries. Want to find another time?" One message. Then leave it.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sop-sec-label">Rules</div>
  <div class="rules-row">
    <span class="rule-tag hard">Zoom link sent immediately — not later</span>
    <span class="rule-tag hard">Reminder evening before — not morning of</span>
    <span class="rule-tag">Hand-off needs context, not just a name</span>
    <span class="rule-tag">No-show: one follow-up only</span>
  </div>
